{"lastModified":1774622040541,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nExperience luxury aboard the Lagoon 52 F Akana, perfect for up to 10 guests. With 5 spacious cabins it offers all the comforts of home, including 5 bathrooms with showers and full bedding.\n\nAkana is equipped with modern sailing features, including radar, GPS plotter, and generator, along with air conditioning, heating, and an audio system with outside speakers. The fully-equipped galley includes a fridge, oven, coffee machine, and ice maker, ensuring you have everything you need for a relaxing cruise.\n\nSet sail along Croatia’s stunning coast for an unforgettable experience on Akana.","blueprint":{"name":"AKANA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::iiZzuQ-9i.png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-70009-full-7072_brochure_1_jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7725-hiog7WCJh.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7725-ENtK8r4yAu.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-69794-full-nicer_png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-69792-full-nice_png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7725-eEcliy5GE.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7725-RyQU2UwGGH.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7725-gGMs22Aee0.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::y