{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"Wake Board ","quantity":"1"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"0"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Sea Bobs"}],"entertainment":["Onboard WIFI","Flat-screen TV","Bluetooth sound system","Board Games"],"tenders":["Highfield 3.60m 20hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Davor Mioković|","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5d7d2d50-9930-11f0-bad9-c5d238cbdc1c/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born: 1980 Nation: Croatian | Languages: English, Croatian\n\nDavor is an energetic and personable professional with a strong passion for boats and maritime activities. He is the kind of captain who instantly puts everyone at ease. With nearly two decades of experience on catamarans throughout the Mediterranean – including the Lagoon 620 and 560 – he’s known for his calm presence, sharp navigation skills, and genuine care for both his crew and guests. With a natural ability to read people and anticipate their needs, he ensures every journey is memorable. Thrives in high-energy environments and is deeply passionate about adrenaline-driven sports and outdoor adventures.\n"},{"name":"Una Rogulja","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3c3-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::805ca300-9930-11f0-bad9-c5d238cbdc1c/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born: 1979 | Nation: Croatian\nLanguages: English / Croatian\n\nUna’s journey began in the arts, with a foundation in dance and over a decade of experience as a stained glass and jewellery designer. But eleven years ago, Una followed her heart to the sea, beginning a new chapter as a yacht hostess. She blends her artistic eye with a deep love for maritime life, delivering exceptional and personalised experiences to guests aboard.\nUna has a flair for Mediterranean cuisine: simple, fresh, beautifully presented and she’s just as comfortable preparing a light lunch under sail as she is curating a special dinner onboard. Her experience spans both high-end charters and hostess training, and she always brings a calm, joyful energy to the yacht. Guests love her attentiveness, eye for detail, and ability to make them feel completely at home.\n"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1950000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1950000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2350000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2350000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"High Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2350000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2350000,"amount":2350000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.13}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.25,"unitPrice":2350000,"amount":587500}],"total":3243000,"subTotal":2937500,"totalTax":305500},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Croatia","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Croatia"],"coordinates":[16.818610292079534,44.700266827856225],"bbox":[13.517187500000006,42.432910156249996,19.400976562500006,46.534619140625]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"Mid Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2150000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice"